highlights.text: “八方來財(Stacks from All Sides)” by 攬佬SKAI ISYOURGOD has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 155 days straight.
ATLXS has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “PASSO BEM SOLTO - Slowed” is the highest at #14.
“Eyes, Nose, Lips (Hardstyle Mix)” by KICKCHEEZE is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 34 spots at #36.
